          </div>
          <h2 class="mb-6">A Day at NewBridge Living</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
            Our structured daily schedule provides the framework for building healthy habits and sustainable recovery routines.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-20 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0A2A4A]">6:00 AM</div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium mb-1">Morning Wake-Up</div>
